---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - CoursesWyn"
  description="Learn about CoursesWyn's privacy practices, how we handle your data, and our affiliate disclosure for Udemy courses and free coupons."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8">
    <header class="space-y-3">
      <p class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-purple-100 text-purple-800">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        CoursesWyn respects your privacy while publishing independent Udemy reviews and affiliate links.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-purple-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-900">1. Information we collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
        <li>Email address via contact form (only if you send us a message).</li>
        <li>Analytics data (page views, referrer, country) via Vercel Speed Insights.</li>
        <li>No personal data is collected automatically or stored without consent.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-900">2. How we use information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
        <li>To respond to your questions or corrections about Udemy reviews.</li>
        <li>To improve site performance and content relevance via anonymized analytics.</li>
        <li>We never sell, rent, or share your email with third parties.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-900">3. Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        CoursesWyn includes Udemy affiliate links. If you purchase through these links, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
        This does not influence which courses we review or rank.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-900">4. Cookies and tracking</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
        <li>Essential cookies for site functionality (e.g., theme preference).</li>
        <li>Analytics cookies via Vercel Speed Insights (aggregated, anonymized).</li>
        <li>No advertising or third-party tracking cookies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-900">5. Your rights</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
        <li>Request a copy of any data we hold about you.</li>
        <li>Ask us to delete your data (contact form or corrections@courseswyn.com).</li>
        <li>Opt out of analytics by disabling JavaScript or using a blocker.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-900">6. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here with an updated date.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-purple-600">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
